ClickHouse increase `ReplicatedPartFailedFetches` in `system.events` table.
It mean server was failed to download data part from replica of a ReplicatedMergeTree table.
Please check following things:
- connections between ClickHouse pod and his replicas (see remote_server section in /etc/clickhouse-server/)
- [logs](/#/components/{{ componentUrnForUrl }}#logs) of the pod